---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Catálogo"
  description="Catálogo de productos Grupo METRO — Bebidas, refrescos, cervezas, aguas, licores y más. Precios actualizados Junio 2026."
>

<!-- ═══════ HERO ═══════ -->
<section class="hero-bg pt-20 pb-12 sm:pt-28 sm:pb-16 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10 reveal">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 mb-8" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors">Inicio</a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
      <span class="text-zinc-300">Catálogo</span>
    </nav>
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-6">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-red"></span>
      <span class="text-zinc-300 text-xs tracking-wider uppercase font-medium">Junio 2026</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="font-display text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl leading-[1.0] uppercase tracking-tight">Catálogo</h1>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-4 sm:mt-5 max-w-lg mx-auto text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Consulta todos nuestros productos, formatos y precios actualizados. Nuevas referencias cada mes.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════ PDF — Dark ═══════ -->
<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-[var(--color-dark-alt)] relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center reveal">
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <span class="text-brand-red text-xs sm:text-sm tracking-[.3em] uppercase font-semibold">Descarga</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-white mt-3 mb-5 leading-[1.1] uppercase tracking-tight">Catálogo Completo</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-lg">
          Nuestro catálogo incluye todos los productos disponibles con sus precios actualizados (IVA incluido).
          Ábrelo en una pestaña nueva o descárgalo para consultarlo cuando quieras.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <a href="/catalogo-junio-2026.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-red text-white px-8 py-4 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm hover:bg-brand-red-dark transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
            Abrir Catálogo PDF
            <span class="inline-block transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5" aria-hidden="true">&#8599;</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/catalogo-junio-2026.pdf" download
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-white/15 text-white px-8 py-4 text-sm tracking-wider uppercase hover:border-brand-red/50 hover:text-brand-red transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"/></svg>
            Descargar PDF
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-xs text-zinc-500">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg> 47 páginas</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg> Precios + IVA</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1"><svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg> Actualizado Junio 2026</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card preview — sin puntitos de tráfico -->
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="bg-[var(--color-dark-card)] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[var(--shadow-xl)]">
          <div class="p-8 text-center">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-brand-red mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
            <img src="/logo.jpg" alt="Grupo METRO" class="w-full max-w-[160px] mx-auto rounded-lg mb-4" loading="lazy" width="200" height="100" />
            <p class="text-white text-sm font-semibold">Catálogo Junio 2026</p>
            <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-1">Formato PDF · 47 páginas · Precios + IVA</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════ CATEGORÍAS — Gris claro ═══════ -->
<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-[var(--color-light-alt)] relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-14 reveal">
      <span class="text-brand-red text-xs sm:text-sm tracking-[.3em] uppercase font-semibold">Productos</span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-[var(--color-text-dark)] mt-3 mb-4 leading-[1.1] uppercase tracking-tight">¿Qué Encontrarás?</h2>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-sm sm:text-base max-w-lg mx-auto">Cinco categorías con las marcas más demandadas por hostelería y retail en Tarragona.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4 sm:gap-5 reveal">
      <!-- Refrescos -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-[var(--color-light-border)] rounded-xl p-5 sm:p-6 text-center shadow-[var(--shadow-sm)] hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-md)] hover:border-brand-red/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-xl bg-brand-red/5 flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src="/logos/Coca-Cola.svg" alt="" class="h-10 w-auto object-contain" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-dark)] text-sm mb-1.5">Refrescos</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-xs leading-relaxed">Coca-Cola, Fanta, Nestea, Don Simon, Granini, Juver</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Aguas -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-[var(--color-light-border)] rounded-xl p-5 sm:p-6 text-center shadow-[var(--shadow-sm)] hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-md)] hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-xl bg-brand-blue/5 flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src="/logos/Evian.svg" alt="" class="h-10 w-auto object-contain" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-dark)] text-sm mb-1.5">Aguas</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-xs leading-relaxed">Font Vella, Evian, Bezoya, Viladrau, Solán de Cabras, Perrier, San Pellegrino, Vichy Catalan</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Cervezas -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-[var(--color-light-border)] rounded-xl p-5 sm:p-6 text-center shadow-[var(--shadow-sm)] hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-md)] hover:border-brand-red/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-xl bg-brand-red/5 flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src="/logos/Heineken.svg" alt="" class="h-10 w-auto object-contain" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-dark)] text-sm mb-1.5">Cervezas</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-xs leading-relaxed">Estrella Damm, Heineken, Mahou, San Miguel, Corona, Budweiser, Guinness, Alhambra</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Licores -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-[var(--color-light-border)] rounded-xl p-5 sm:p-6 text-center shadow-[var(--shadow-sm)] hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-md)] hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-xl bg-brand-blue/5 flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src="/logos/Brugal.png" alt="" class="h-10 w-auto object-contain" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-dark)] text-sm mb-1.5">Licores</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-xs leading-relaxed">Brugal, Larios, Bodega Pinord, Kopparberg, Strongbow, Magners</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Energéticas -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-[var(--color-light-border)] rounded-xl p-5 sm:p-6 text-center shadow-[var(--shadow-sm)] hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-md)] hover:border-brand-red/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-xl bg-brand-red/5 flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src="/logos/Red-Bull.svg" alt="" class="h-10 w-auto object-contain" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-dark)] text-sm mb-1.5">Energéticas</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-xs leading-relaxed">Red Bull, Powerking, Monster</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════ CÓMO PEDIR — Dark ═══════ -->
<section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-[var(--color-dark-alt)] relative">
  <!-- Línea geométrica -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-48 h-48 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" class="w-full h-full opacity-[0.03]">
      <line x1="200" y1="0" x2="0" y2="200" stroke="#d9445a" stroke-width="1" />
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10 reveal">
    <span class="text-brand-red text-xs sm:text-sm tracking-[.3em] uppercase font-semibold">Pedidos</span>
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-white mt-3 mb-5 leading-[1.1] uppercase tracking-tight">¿Cómo Pedir?</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 text-base max-w-lg mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
      Contacta con nosotros por WhatsApp y te preparamos el pedido. Sin aplicaciones, sin registros, sin esperas.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10 text-left">
      <div class="bg-[var(--color-dark-card)] border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-brand-red text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white text-sm font-semibold">Escríbenos</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Cuéntanos qué productos necesitas y cantidades.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[var(--color-dark-card)] border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-brand-blue text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white text-sm font-semibold">Presupuesto</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Te confirmamos precios y disponibilidad al momento.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[var(--color-dark-card)] border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-5 flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-brand-red text-white flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</span>
        <div>
          <p class="text-white text-sm font-semibold">Entrega</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-0.5">Recíbelo en tu negocio. Rápido y sin complicaciones.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="https://wa.me/34600781881" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-red text-white px-10 py-5 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm hover:bg-brand-red-dark transition-colors">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
      Pedir por WhatsApp
    </a>
    <p class="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-4">+34 600 781 881 · Respuesta rápida garantizada</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════ NAVEGACIÓN CRUZADA — Blanco ═══════ -->
<section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-[var(--color-light)] border-t border-[var(--color-light-border)]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-brand-red transition-colors text-sm font-medium group">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"/></svg>
        Volver al inicio
      </a>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-xs">¿Tienes alguna pregunta sobre nuestros productos?</p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/34600781881" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-red hover:text-brand-red-dark transition-colors text-sm font-semibold mt-1">
          Contáctanos por WhatsApp <span aria-hidden="true">&#8599;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <a href="/#quienes-somos" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-brand-red transition-colors text-sm font-medium group">
        Quiénes Somos
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
